        <abstract> 
<p>CD hopes the <hi rend="italic">Times</hi> abstract of minutes of Lords of the Treasury will make JDH’s position more comfortable.</p> 
            <p>The "wretched Lords" make CD indignant, but "nothing equals Owen’s conduct. – I used to be ashamed of hating him so much, but now I will carefully cherish my hatred &amp; contempt to the last day of my life."</p>
        </abstract>
